Package calculation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Calculations
    Calculations The model of the calculations - contains all variables from input, calculates for the wanted variable, and provides needed values for animation
    CalculationsPanel
    CalculationsPanel The view showing the process work of the calculation for the wanted variable
    GivensPanel
    GivensPanel The view showing the variables and values that the user inputs
    ProcessFrame
    ProcessFrame The main view of the calculations - contains the individual panels showing givens/calculation process and the save button
    ProcessSaveController
    ProcessSaveController The controller that saves the process work of the calculation used to get the wanted variable
